version 2.0.1
--------------
* Now bot can move him self to background
* Indicate when bot connected on the console
* Responding on ctcp version.
* New plugin handler: unloader_<plugin-name> - Will execute code before unloading the plugin.
* Bot will create the 'logs' directory if necessary.
* Errors logging is replacing the admin logger
* Admins commands had changed, please see the README file.
* New Plugins.
* Fixing factoids (liel's plugin) to remove all commands on unloading
* Bug Fixes



